@43   = ~The Argent Shield +4~
@44   = ~This silver shield once resided in the Hand of the Seldarine, where it was used to protect its bearer from harmful magic and attacks. Because of its racial attunement, the marauding orcs and goblins left it in the tower. Maiden Ilmadia grabbed it from the ruins.

