@45   = ~Arrow of the Hand +8~
@46   = ~Made during the golden age between the elves of the Seldarine's Hand and the dwarves of Dorn's Deep. Any expert fletcher will find these to be some of the finest arrows ever made. They are weighted and balanced perfectly and can pierce through the strongest armor.

