@65   = ~Morohanotsurugi +5~
@66   = ~This weapon originally belonged to a local Kara-Tur liege-lord, Yodama Akira, who burned one of the villages under his protection to the ground on a perceived slight from the peasants. Though within Yodama's rights as liege-lord, the act deeply shamed Yodama's daimyo, who commissioned Morohanotsurugi, the double-edged sword, as a result. Morohanotsurugi was given to Yodama to teach him a simple lesson: harming others should never be without consequence. 

STATISTICS:

Cursed:
