@78   = ~Crafted by a powerful invoker, the Bracers of Blasting are dangerous tools for mages strong enough to use them. There are a number of these sets of bracers floating around Faerun, and they circulate very quickly, as the mages who put them on tend not to live much longer. The creator of these bronze armbands has been lost to history.

