@89   = ~Wyvern Riders of the Hand

Stationed atop Shevarash Tower are the magnificent wyverns of the Seldarine's Hand. Along with their riders, these mounts serve primarily as scouts but are sometimes used for missions requiring the utmost of speed.

Both rider and mount are trained rigorously to work as a team. Upon hatching, wyverns are domesticated to be used as mounts. They are trained in what to eat, various combat routines involving aerial and ground attacks, and to respond to the commands of its rider. The rider is educated in the ways of grooming and caring for his or her mount, how to work effectively with it, and also in the ways of aerial and ground combat. As a unit, they have proven excellent aerial support in our ground battles and are a proud symbol of the Seldarine.

The wyvern trainers of the Hand are renowned for their skill in overcoming the wyvern's violent temperament and turning it into a reliable ally. However, if a domesticated wyvern were to be left unattended for even a few weeks, it would surely become feral once more.~
