@138  = ~This mage robe has been perfected for use by any itinerant mage that travels from town to town. Its enchantments provide protection from the bandit's arrow and from the jealous mage/thief that lies in ambush with his Stinking Cloud. As with other robes of its kind, the Traveler's Robe can only be worn by wizards. 

