@209  = ~An extremely valuable magic item on its own, the Gauntlet of Valor is part of one of only three remaining Power Arms made by the elven archmages of Myth Drannor. The devices were crafted for use by champions defending the ancient elven city on the rare occasions when it was in danger. This eternally shining gauntlet represents a pinnacle of elven craftsmanship and enchantment. Adventurers and ambitious villains across the realms yearn to find the location of all the pieces of the Power Arms.

