@212  = ~Hand of the Gloomfrost +5~
@213  = ~This weapon was fashioned by your hands, guided by the dwarf Tiernon. Forged from ice taken from the walls of the Gloomfrost, this blade has taken some of the glacier and some of your strength into it, creating a formidable weapon. Though made of ice, the weapon is only slightly cold to the touch and does not melt, even when exposed to the hottest flames.

