@298  = ~Nym's Rhino Beetle Shield +3~
@299  = ~This shield was crafted from the exoskeleton of a giant rhinoceros beetle. Naturally tough, it has been cured and reinforced by skilled duergar craftsmen. It looks and functions like a tower shield crafted from wood and metal, though it weighs much less. Most importantly, the shield retains some of the rhinoceros beetle's ability to reflect missiles and spells aimed at it. Dark elven sorcerers have added enchantments to this particular shield, greatly increasing the protection it provides.

