@306  = ~Originally crafted for a master thief, this deep red ioun stone was found-along with most of a gnome's skull-inside the shell of a giant clam off the Sword Coast. Although its power has since been used in more noble causes by hunters, weavers, and one particularly vain harpist, the stone remains an invaluable asset to those of a less honorable bent.

