@1181 = ~Offensive Spin

During the next 4 rounds, the character's movement rate doubles and <PRO_HESHE> gains a +2 bonus to hit and damage rolls as well as an extra attack per round. All attacks deal maximum damage for the duration. Offensive Spin may be used in conjunction with the Haste or Improved Haste spells.~
@1182 = ~Summon Spirit Animal

