@1183 = ~Storm Shield

This spell lasts 5 rounds plus 1 round per level of the caster. It protects the caster completely from lightning, fire, cold, and normal missiles. In addition, the caster is protected from harmful storm and cloud spells and abilities, including Stinking Cloud, Writhing Fog, Ice Storm, Auril's Blizzard, Cloud of Pestilence, Cloudkill, Death Fog, Whirlwind, Acid Storm, Fire Storm, Stygian Ice Storm, Storm of Vengeance, Incendiary Cloud, Malavon's Corrosive Fog, Great Tornado, Greater Ghast Stench, Hell Cloud, Festering Drowned Dead auras. Beneficial spells of those types like Cloudburst and Mist of Eldath still affect the caster. Chain Lightning will not jump to the caster unless the caster was the original target.~
